---
By: Ralph W. Trine
Locus:
  Page: 309
  Verse: 18
Tags:
  - Love
---
Put love into the world and heavenwith all its beauties and gloriesbecomes
a reality. Not to love is not tolive, or to live a living death. The
lifethat goes out in love to all is the lifethat is full, and rich, and
continuallyexpanding in beauty and in power.
